HEADWORD: Snarler
<hw>Snarl"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who snarls; a
surly, growling animal; a grumbling, quarrelsome fellow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snarler</ent>⟦br⟧

